The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization of submodular functions (cs.DS) and approximation algorithms (cs.AI). The online setting is also considered, which falls under the category of online algorithms (cs.LG) and information theory (cs.IT).
